My anxiety and panic is at a 100 plus nowdays bc of all the what if‚Äôs and unknowns. I think everyone‚Äôs like this but for us it‚Äôs debilitating for sure. I‚Äôm isolating under my blanket, can‚Äôt breathe, heart rate way up, insomnia, and exhausted mentally. I did this today, learned in BPD to ask if these feelings are founded. I‚Äôd say yes haha. What you are feeling is ok. You‚Äôre not wrong, worthless, or deserving of anything bad. A thought is just a thought. It‚Äôs what you do that matters. I self harm to cope and yes that‚Äôs not healthy but it what‚Äôs I know. Just like people who do drugs. Now theresradical acceptance. That things are what they are and it is what it is. We will just adjust and handle each situation as it comes up. Honestly, I‚Äôve thought if I get sick , I get sick. Of course I gonna do all the recommended things for virus protection but I‚Äôve accepted what will or may happen . But hopefully we‚Äôll all be ok haha.

Thank you! Ya I just thought I was the coolest chick, everyone else was lame, I was the life of the party, and reeeeaaallll popular with the boys . I was the class slut. All my ways I realize now because of wanting love and attention to make me feel good. I‚Äôve had some very difficult years, rape, suicidal events, self harm, short lived relationships, and heavy drug use. I‚Äôve gotten thru all that , I mean I‚Äôm still here but still having to deal with the disease. Knowing that what it was is how I know how to handle things better by going to DBT classes, a psychologist every week. And a psychiatrist once a month. For the last 4 years. Don‚Äôt get me wrong I still freak out, cut, scream, and have dark thoughts constantly but I acknowledge them then move on. May be the next hour or day but it happens again and again. Your thoughts aren‚Äôt bad or wrong, theyre how you feel. It‚Äôs ok. You‚Äôre young and I won‚Äôt sugar coat it , it‚Äôs a long hard road. But hopefully things will happen that will bring you help and most important as it was for me finding my Husband who I‚Äôve been with for 25 years and has put up with all my disasters.  Take care.
